like ChatGPT and Google Bard,

5
00:00:06.004 --> 00:00:08.004
and that's to establish roles.

6
00:00:08.004 --> 00:00:11.005
What that means is you can assign a role

7
00:00:11.005 --> 00:00:14.001
that the AI tool is going to play

8
00:00:14.001 --> 00:00:16.009
and you can also assign a role that you yourself,

9
00:00:16.009 --> 00:00:19.005
as the receiver of the information, is going to play.

10
00:00:19.005 --> 00:00:20.009
So check out this example.

11
