What's the best way to clean data?

12
00:00:22.008 --> 00:00:25.002
ChatGPT comes back with a response here,

13
00:00:25.002 --> 00:00:27.005
but then we can add so much more context

14
00:00:27.005 --> 00:00:29.009
in terms of the role that we are going to be playing,

15
00:00:29.009 --> 00:00:32.005
a new Data Analyst for a retail business.

16
00:00:32.005 --> 00:00:35.000
And then we want the AI tool to play the role

17
