of a Data QA Engineer and provide a step-by-step plan

18
00:00:38.007 --> 00:00:40.000
that we can follow.

19
00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.009
So when we establish these roles,

20
00:00:41.009 --> 00:00:44.002
it's more clear to the AI tool

21
00:00:44.002 --> 00:00:46.005
exactly who the audience is,

22
00:00:46.005 --> 00:00:49.008
what you want to be getting in your response,

23
